name: Experiment Or Die Airdrop #1
description: Month 1 of Experiment or Die consisted of 31 original collages and this piece is a mash-up of all the pieces that were sold during the first month. This piece will be airdropped to each of the collectors and is a special thanks for being early supporters. 11 separate pieces were purchased during month 1. Ig and Twitter: @Nikejerk
